%h2.posting Create a Posting - Postings will automatically expire after thirty minutes.  

%p
  Not sure what to work on but you want to work on something?  Check out
  = link_to 'Project Euler', 'http://projecteuler.net/', :target => '_blank'
  and
  = link_to 'Code Katas', 'http://codekata.pragprog.com/', :target => '_blank'
  
#posting-area
  = simple_form_for @posting do |f|
  
    = render "shared/error_messages", :target => @posting
        
    = f.input :email, :hint => 'not shown', :error => false
    = f.input :display_name, :hint => 'optional'
    = f.input :idea, :error => false
  
    = f.association :languages, :collection => Language.all(:order => 'name'), :as => :check_boxes, :error => false

    = f.button :submit
    
%p.idea
  Postings will automatically expire after thirty minutes.